summary: An email from an FBI Special Agent in the New York Field Office transmitting a federal trial subpoena to AT&T for records, indicating an ongoing legal proceeding related to child exploitation or human trafficking.

persons.name: Special Agen
persons.context: Sends an email with a federal trial subpoena attachment to AT&T, requesting an expeditious response for records.

events.title: Issuance of Federal Trial Subpoena to AT&T
events.description: A federal trial subpoena is issued to AT&T for records, as indicated by the attached PDF filename.

keyFacts: A federal trial subpoena was issued to AT&T for records on or around November 11, 2021.
The subpoena is related to an FBI investigation in the New York Field Office focusing on Child Exploitation/Human Trafficking.
The communication emphasizes the importance and urgency of the request for an expeditious response.
